</emphasis>
Adults of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3030F42860FFCDFECA8797E0D26CD1" box="[381,503,2005,2027]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Fragilonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="42" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. n.">
